703101f-a.text:
Bath Ave., north side, between Bay 19th and [Bay] 22nd Streets. A view of the Bensonhurst station of the Brooklyn Bath and West End R.R. Teh two homes at the right, face 19th Ave; the home in the back right, seen between the two homes, faces Bay 22nd Street. In the background, is Benson Ave. 1888.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

Neg. #4701
